Package: modelscloud
Title: R Interface for the ModelsCloud Platform
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mohsen", "Sadatsafavi", email = "mohsen.sadatsafavi@ubc.ca",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A high-level R interface for accessing models hosted on the
    ModelsCloud platform (modelscloud.resp.core.ubc.ca). Wraps the pexaclient
    package to provide a session-based, model-centric workflow: connect once
    with connect_to_model(), then call model_run(), get_default_input(), and
    get_sample_input() without repeating credentials or model paths.
